Summary: Two Oval Shaped Objects Over Cementary...
divs: Sighting DetailsI took this pic back in 05 while visiting my decease parents at mesa city cementary, on top left corner of pic theres two oval shaped objects, i was leaving the cementary at the time i took this pic, if you look straight down the road you will see hohokom park, home of the Chicago cubs spring training, but there was nothing going on there at the time, spring training had ended, and when i took this pic there was nothing there in the sky at the time...
